<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>﴿أَلَمْ تَرَ﴾<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> ﴿أَبَابِيلَ﴾ مُتَتَابِعَةً مُجْتَمِعَةً.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> ﴿مِنْ سِجِّيلٍ﴾ هِيَ سَنْكِ وَكِلْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>